title: Toto & Friends - 1992-12-14 - Tribute Concert, Universal Amp

LINEAGE
I didn't do the original work on this, I am reposting here in response to a request on the ISO board. This 
version is courtesy of JDouglee who has confirmed:

The lineage is DAT > CDR > EAC > Cool Edit > FLAC. It was remastered, i.e. tranferred from one of the original DAT tapes given to the band. The old version circulating was a flawed radio broadcast. This is indeed the best version available anywhere."
